## Project Title

GBDA302 Week 6 Example 4 with added sound effects and background music

---

## Authors

Karen Cochrane and David Han
Modified by Marine-Chloe Vandame using Claude

---

## Description

This p5.js project is a pixel-art 2D platformer game where you play as a fox navigating through a tilemap-based level. The objective of the game is to collect 15 leaves to win the game while avoiding boars that patrol the level and attacks.

---

## Learning Goals

- To add sounds to our sketches.js triggered by motion, collisions or from player action.

---

